    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work or can be used for parts. The exterior has extensive rust, several large dents, and the paint is heavily faded. Mechanically, it currently does not run reliably and will likely need a new transmission and major engine repairs. The interior shows heavy wear, with torn seating and a non-functional dashboard. It is sold strictly as-is.",
