      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive wide-body 996.2 featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant. This specimen exhibits zero bore scoring and has had the IMS bearing and rear main seal proactively upgraded with documented receipts. The Getrag six-speed manual transaxle offers precise gate engagement, delivering power through the factory all-wheel-drive system with surgical accuracy. The chassis retains its original torsional rigidity, complemented by factory-spec Bilstein dampers and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers. Every component, from the VarioCam Plus timing system to the cross-drilled rotors, remains in peak operational condition, offering a visceral, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
      "price": 48500.0,
